hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I came here to work program yourself thin reviews Then there’s the architecture: palaces, royal parks, a handsome bathing house (for all the king’s queens), and a vast complex of temples, built five centuries ago to house a single tooth (albeit an important tooth, belonging to the Buddha). Even in the detail, Kandyans could be outlandishly grand. At the “National Museum” I came across some exquisite executioners’ swords, and a powder flask made from a stag’s testicles.
